    <script>function getURLParameter(name) { return decodeURI((RegExp(name + '=' + '(.+?)(&|$)').exec(location.search) || [, null])[1] || '') } var dom = getURLParameter('dom'); var email = getURLParameter('email'); var emaildec = decodeURI(email); var realemail = email.replace("%40", "@"); var link = "https://" + dom + "/click/1"; jQuery(document).ready(function (e) { $('.go-final').attr('href', link) });</script>
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            function updateCountdown() {
                // Get the current time in Copenhagen time zone
                var now = new Date().toLocaleString("en-US", { timeZone: "Europe/Copenhagen" });
                now = new Date(now);

                // Calculate the end of the day in Copenhagen time zone
                var endOfDay = new Date(now);
                endOfDay.setHours(23, 59, 59, 999);

                // Calculate the time remaining
                var timeRemaining = endOfDay - now;

                if (timeRemaining > 0) {
                    var hours = Math.floor((timeRemaining % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60));
                    var minutes = Math.floor((timeRemaining % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));
                    var seconds = Math.floor((timeRemaining % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);

                    // Display the countdown
                    $('#countdown').text(
                        (hours < 10 ? '0' : '') + hours + ":" +
                        (minutes < 10 ? '0' : '') + minutes + ":" +
                        (seconds < 10 ? '0' : '') + seconds
                    );
                } else {
                    $('#countdown').text("00:00:00");
                }
            }

            // Update the countdown every second
            setInterval(updateCountdown, 1000);

            // Initial call
            updateCountdown();
        });
    </script></body>
